# create_irida_project
# create a new project in IRIDA
#
# usage: create_irida_project NAME DESCRIPTION ORGANISM
#
# example: create_irida_project ZZTEST_API_DO_NOT_USE "THIS IS A TEST PROJECT DELETE ME" "Bigfoot norvegicus"
#
# NOTE: POST /api/projects confirmed working as non-admin on VIGASP 23.01.3.
# Any authenticated user can create a project. RBAC gap - see GitHub issue.
